<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .button { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .success { background: #D1FAE5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            <div class="success">
                <strong>Your payment of ${{amount}} was successful!</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Thank you for subscribing to Flowvera <strong>{{plan}}</strong> plan. Your payment has been processed successfully.</p>
            <p>You now have full access to all features included in your plan. Continue managing your projects and growing your business with Flowvera!</p>
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            <p>You'll receive a receipt for this payment shortly.</p>
            <p><strong>The Flowvera Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Flowvera. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
